Properties.Caption: Просмотр отчетов об исполнении бюджета субъекта-доходы
Properties.Tag: Select [K_TD].[CTD] As [Тип документа], Max([K_TD].[NTD]) As [Наименование типа документа], [Apps_Groups].[GroupName] As [Группа], [DOC].[CDOC] As [Документ], [K_TD_SUB].[CTD_SUB] As [Подтип], Max([K_TD_SUB].[NTD_SUB]) As [Наименование подтипа], [REP_DESC].[CODE1] As [КОД1], Max([REP_DESC].[NAME]) As [Наименование показателя], [REP_DESC].[CODE2] As [КОД2], Sum([REP].[SUMM02]) As [Графа 02], Sum([REP].[SUMM04]) As [Графа 04], Sum([REP].[SUMM03]) As [Графа 03], Sum([REP].[SUMM06]) As [Графа 06], Sum([REP].[SUMM08]) As [Графа 08], Sum([REP].[SUMM07]) As [Графа 07], Sum([REP].[SUMM01]) As [Графа 01], Sum([REP].[SUMM15]) As [Графа 15], Sum([REP].[SUMM05]) As [Графа 05], Sum([REP].[SUMM16]) As [Графа 16] From (((((((((([REP] With (NoLock) Inner Join [DOC] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[DOCID]=[DOC].[DOCID])) Inner Join [Apps_Groups] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[Apps_GroupsID]=[Apps_Groups].[Apps_GroupsID])) Inner Join [K_UL_K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[K_UL_K_ULID]=[K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([K_UL_K_UL].[K_ULID]=[K_UL].[K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_UL] As [K_UL_PARENT] With (NoLock) On ([K_UL_K_UL].[K_ULID_PARENT]=[K_UL_PARENT].[K_ULID])) Inner Join [Apps_Groups_K_UL_K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID]=[Apps_Groups_K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID])) Inner Join [REP_DESC] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[REP_DESCID]=[REP_DESC].[REP_DESCID])) Inner Join [K_PERIOD] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[K_PERIODID]=[K_PERIOD].[K_PERIODID])) Inner Join [K_TD_SUB] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[K_TD_SUBID]=[K_TD_SUB].[K_TD_SUBID])) Inner Join [K_TD] With (NoLock) On ([K_TD_SUB].[K_TDID]=[K_TD].[K_TDID])) Where [Apps_Groups_K_UL_K_UL].[Apps_GroupsID]=GetApps_GroupsID() And [K_TD_SUB].[CTD_SUB] In ('161','163','164','166') And [REP].[SUMM_TYPE]=0 And |0 Group by [K_TD].[CTD], [Apps_Groups].[GroupName], [DOC].[CDOC], [K_TD_SUB].[CTD_SUB], [REP_DESC].[CODE1], [REP_DESC].[CODE2] Order by |1
Properties.Name: Просмотр отчетов об исполнении бюджета субъекта-доходы
